            <title>[LU-4144] Run IOR in data check mode in parallel-scale</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4144</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It appears we&apos;re missing an opportunity to do some data verification testing when we run IOR in parallel-scale and parallel-scale-nfs. Since we&apos;re not tracking the performance of these runs, we might as well use the checkWrite and checkRead options so IOR does data checking for us.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
